name: Reynold Anderson
description: Well as for me I’m a nice,caring, straight forward and loving man that says what’s on my mind,I am an emotional,caring and loving person that’s not infatuated in woman but want the true love that she has toward i have been..I’m cool headed, lovable and very friendly kid that is associates with people and doesn’t shy off…I enjoy traveling when ever I can. I enjoy reading very much Nicholas Sparks, Nora Roberts,Steven King and Dean Koontz,Horror. I have never scuba dived, but I love to snorkel and have swam with stingrays and dolphins, which I would love to do again someday.
